Description: The excelerate package simplifies the creation of supplementary 
    tables for research papers. It uses the openxlsx R package to produce tables 
    in a consistent format. You can easily turn data frames into Excel files, 
    with accompanying metadata in a README sheet, and save them as numbered 
    supplementary files.
